window-reveal: 0.01
window-height: 0.4
depth: 0.15
animation: true

panel-1
=======
A red square.

animation
=========
type: loop
t_max: 5
start: rotation angle is 0
end: rotation angle is 360
autostart: true
Rotate the square around its center.

dashboard
=========
size: slider. min=50px, max=500px. The view is numerical. Sets the side length of the square in panel-1. Live update.
color: knob. Continuous. The view should just show the currently selected color. Live update.
